status_message:
Breaking News Update: A shootout on the Champs-Élysées in Paris left at least one policeman dead and 2 wounded. The attack comes days before an election.

We'll be updating here: http://nyti.ms/2o968es

On this day in 2004, Thefacebook.com made its debut. Read an article about Facebook in The Times from that year in which Peter Applebome describes the social network a "Swiss Army knife of procrastination": http://nyti.ms/1euYePd
